# ğŸ› AI-DBUG

**An AI-powered Python debugger that explains errors in plain English with suggested fixes.**

Stop wasting time deciphering cryptic error messages! AI-DBUG translates Python errors into clear, understandable explanations with practical solutions.

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ¯ **Automatic Error Capture** - Hooks into Python's exception system
- ğŸ’¡ **Plain English Explanations** - No more cryptic error messages
- ğŸ”§ **Practical Fix Suggestions** - Step-by-step solutions for 70+ error types
- ğŸ¨ **Beautiful Output** - Colored, formatted error messages
- ğŸŒ **Cross-Platform** - Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux
- ğŸ–¥ï¸ **IDE Compatible** - VS Code, PyCharm, Jupyter, and all terminals
- ğŸ“š **Extensive Knowledge Base** - Covers almost all Python error types
- ğŸ”Œ **One-Line Setup** - Get started in seconds

